  "text": "SPEA2 The SPEA2 algorithm [CITATION_1] chosen to represent CB methods. It is a multi-objective optimization algorithm incorporating concepts initially used in OptGene [CITATION_2] . Similarly to other bi-level heuristic frameworks, the inner problem pertains the assessment of the quality of the solution. However, unlike other algorithms, it can assume multiple objectives. In this case, the objective is the maximization of two objective functions, namely biomass and product flux. Parsimonious FBA (pFBA) [CITATION_3] is used to obtain both these values.",
